## n8n@0.92.0 For a comprehensive list of changes, check out the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.91.0...n8n@0.92.0) for this version.
**Release date:** 2020-11-04 - New nodes - Facebook Trigger - Google Books - Orbit - Storyblok - Enhanced nodes - Google Drive: Removed duplicate parameters - Twitter: Added Direct Message resource - Bug Fixes - Gmail: Fixed an issue with the encoding for the subject field - Improved the Editor UI for the save workflow functionality
